## PHQ-9 vs DASI

PHQ-9 vs DASI Psychologists often come across the necessity to compare different questionnaires like PHQ-9 and DASI. These two key psychometric instruments help in assessing mental health but come with distinct sets of questions focusing on different aspects. Instead of running through the questions manually, using software like Harmony can simplify this tedious task. The innovative software tool, Harmony, can help immensely in this Harmonisation process. When comparing PHQ-9 vs DASI, Harmony scans through each question of both the tools, giving a percentage match between each item in PHQ-9 and DASI. This quantitative approach can guide researchers in identifying the common points of intersection and the unique elements present in each questionnaire.
